<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>{% block title %}ASSOCIA'LYON{% endblock %}</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-ggOyR0iXCbMQv3Xipma34MD+dH/1fQ784/j6cY/iJTQUOhcWr7x9JvoRxT2MZw1T"
        crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="{{ asset('dist/css/home.css') }}" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="{{ asset('dist/css/style.css') }}" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lobster+Two:400,700|Merienda">


    {% block stylesheets %}{% endblock %}
</head>
<header class="py-2">
    <div class="container-fluid mb-5" id="cover">

        <div class="container text-center">
            <h1 class="pb-3" style="font-size: calc(16px + 1.7vw);">ASSOCIA'LYON</h1>
            <p class="pb-3" style="font-size: calc(10px + 1.2vw);">Agir ensemble pour une ville plus écologique et solidaire</p>

        </div>
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-md navbar-dark">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="#"></a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarSupportedContent"
                aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>

            <div class="d-md-flex justify-content-center collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarSupportedContent">
                    <nav class="site-header sticky-top py-1">
                        <div class="container d-flex flex-column flex-md-row justify-content-between">
                            <a class="nav-link text-info" href="/home">Associa'Lyon</a>
                            <a class="nav-link text-info" href="/proposition">Agir, proposer, collaborer...</a>
                            <a class="nav-link text-info" href="/map">Près de chez vous</a>
                            {% if is_granted('ROLE_USER') %}
                            <a class="nav-link text-info" href="/userui">Mon Espace</a>
                            <a class="nav-link text-info" href="/logout">Déconnexion</a>
                            {% else %}
                            <a class="nav-link text-info" href="/register">S'enregistrer</a>
                            <a class="nav-link text-info" href="/login">Connexion</a>
                            {% endif %}
                        </div>
                    </nav>
                </div> 
        </nav>
</header>
    


<main>
    {% block body %}{% endblock %}
</main>

    <!--FOOTER-->
    <footer class="container-fluid pt-5" id="footer"><hr>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-12 col-md-3 pb-5">
                    <h4>Informations</h4>
                    <nav>
                        <ul>
                            <li><a href="apropos.html">À Propos</a></li>
                            <li><a href="contact.html">Contact</a></li>
                            <li><a href="mentions.html">Dons citoyens</a></li>
                            <li><a href="presse.html">Presse</a></li>
                        </ul>
                    </nav>
                </div>
                <div class="col-12 col-md-3 pb-5">
                    <h4>Réseaux sociaux</h4>
                    <nav>
                        <ul>
                            <li><a href="facebook.html">Facebook</a></li>
                            <li><a href="instagram.html">Instagram</a></li>
                            <li><a href="twitter.html">Twitter</a></li>
                        </ul>
                    </nav>
                </div>
                <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                    <h3>Nos actualités</h3>
                    <p>Abonnez-vous à notre newsletter pour être tenu informé des news d'Associa'Lyon !</p>
                    <p class="error py-3 text-center">Vous n'avez pas rempli correctement le formulaire</p>
                    <form action="newsletter.php" id="newsletter" method="post">
                        <fieldset>
                            <input class="col-12 col-md-6 mb-3" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Adresse E-mail"
                                type="email"></fieldset>
                        <input type="submit" class="text-white bg-secondary" value="VALIDER">
                    </form>
                </div>
                <div class="col-12 pt-4">
                    <p>Pour toute question ou renseignement, nous sommes joignables au 09 81 67 26 81 - du lundi au
                        samedi de 9h30 à 18h00.
                    </p>
                    <p>Un site animé par Associa'Lyon. Images par Jean-Luc Cadrado. Tous droits réservés -
                        2019.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-q8i/X+965DzO0rT7abK41JStQIAqVgRVzpbzo5smXKp4YfRvH+8abtTE1Pi6jizo"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.14.7/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-UO2eT0CpHqdSJQ6hJty5KVphtPhzWj9WO1clHTMGa3JDZwrnQq4sF86dIHNDz0W1"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-JjSmVgyd0p3pXB1rRibZUAYoIIy6OrQ6VrjIEaFf/nJGzIxFDsf4x0xIM+B07jRM"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="{{ asset('/dist/js/script.js') }}"></script>

    {% block javascripts %}{% endblock %}


</html>